(295, 46, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"04059f9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"622a949\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b125d62\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"carousel\":[{\"id\":111,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/6-scaled-1.webp\"},{\"id\":108,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/20220726_092450-scaled.jpg\"},{\"id\":113,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/17eb85dd7352de4.jpg\"},{\"id\":118,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/273750476_247268920911227_7618868633334910557_n.jpg\"}],\"thumbnail_size\":\"ocean-thumb-l\",\"arrows_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":20,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-carousel\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"657e0c3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"060ff14\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"824e15c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Orange Digital Center regroupe sous un m\\u00eame toit quatre programmes strat\\u00e9giques : l\'\\u00e9cole du codage, le FabLab Solidaire, Orange Fab et Orange Digital Ventures Africa. Ce r\\u00e9seau de ressources gratuites et inclusives soutient les start-ups et les projets locaux utilisant la technologie num\\u00e9rique et ils sont d\\u00e9ploy\\u00e9s au Moyen-Orient et en Afrique.<br><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c120a3b\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"30\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"75d4cb3\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3ada2cc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/fab-lab-logo-ours-transparent-2.jpg\",\"id\":88,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"cc2cbaf\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ac30936\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/whatsapp-image-2020-11-27-at-09-56-40.jpeg\",\"id\":89,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f10e089\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"357b5bf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/brief\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/telechargement.png\",\"id\":90,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"79ea9b2\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"30\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"26544b7\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7844c26\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Le FabLab Solidaire est un atelier de production num\\u00e9rique de cr\\u00e9ation et de prototypage avec du mat\\u00e9riel num\\u00e9rique, comme des imprimantes 3D, des fraiseuses et des d\\u00e9coupeuses laser. Il rassemble aussi bien des jeunes ch\\u00f4meurs et sans dipl\\u00f4me que des \\u00e9tudiants, jeunes dipl\\u00f4m\\u00e9s et jeunes entrepreneurs.<\\/p>\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":2,\"blur\":5,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"cb16b32\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"28dcfad\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Orange Digital Kalanso ou l\'\\u00e9cole code\\u00a0 est un p\\u00f4le technologique en libre acc\\u00e8s et totalement gratuit qui propose des formations et des animations \\u00e0 la communaut\\u00e9 des jeunes d\\u00e9veloppeurs, des whiz-kids et des porteurs d\'id\\u00e9es de projets. Il s\'adresse particuli\\u00e8rement aux \\u00e9tudiants, jeunes dipl\\u00f4m\\u00e9s et jeunes entrepreneurs.<\\/p>\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":2,\"blur\":5,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d41c887\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8e61c35\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Orange Fab est un acc\\u00e9l\\u00e9rateur de startups dont l\'objectif est de construire des partenariats commerciaux nationaux et internationaux avec le groupe Orange et le r\\u00e9seau international Orange Fab. Ce programme permet d\'am\\u00e9liorer les capacit\\u00e9s manag\\u00e9riales et d\'accompagner le d\\u00e9veloppement commercial de startups prometteuses et s\'adresse principalement aux entrepreneurs.<\\/p>\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":2,\"blur\":5,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
